---
import cloud from "../assets/sam-cloud.png";
---

<section
	class="relative overflow-hidden border-t-2 border-ink-900 bg-ink-900 text-paper-100"
	id="about"
	aria-labelledby="about-title"
>
	<img
		class="pointer-events-none absolute top-[-3%] left-[3%] h-auto w-[clamp(82px,10vw,145px)] animate-cloud-bob-flip drop-shadow-[0_0_34px_rgb(214_255_63_/_30%)] motion-reduce:animate-none motion-reduce:[transform:scaleX(-1)]"
		src={cloud.src}
		width={cloud.width}
		height={cloud.height}
		alt=""
		aria-hidden="true"
	/>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--container)] px-[var(--gutter)] py-[clamp(80px,10vw,140px)]">
		<p class="eyebrow mb-8 text-volt-500" data-reveal>// about</p>
		<h2
			id="about-title"
			class="mb-10 max-w-[18ch] text-paper-100 tracking-[var(--tracking-tight)] [font:800_clamp(36px,5.5vw,64px)/1.04_var(--font-display)]"
			data-reveal
		>
			I build the <span class="text-volt-500">whole</span> thing, front to back.
		</h2>
		<div
			class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-[clamp(24px,4vw,56px)] max-[640px]:grid-cols-1"
		>
			<p class="m-0 text-ink-200 [font:var(--type-body-lg)]" data-reveal>
				For the last few years I’ve worked across the whole stack, turning rough ideas into products that are fast, reliable, and genuinely useful. Lately that’s meant building internal tools and platforms that quietly cut hours of overhead for the teams using them.
			</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-ink-200 [font:var(--type-body-lg)]" data-reveal>
				I like code that ships, systems that don’t fall over, and the kind of problem where the right fix saves someone a recurring headache. Off the clock you’ll find me over-engineering side projects and pretending that counts as rest.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-[clamp(32px,5vw,64px)]" data-reveal>
			<p class="mb-4 text-ink-400 [font:var(--type-mono-meta)]">tools of the trade</p>
			<ul
				class="m-0 flex flex-wrap gap-[10px] p-0 [list-style:none]"
				aria-label="Technologies I work with"
			>
				{
					[
						"TypeScript",
						"React",
						"Next.js",
						"Remix",
						"Node",
						"GraphQL",
						"Postgres",
						"Azure",
						"Git",
						"Figma",
					].map((tool) => (
						<li class="rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-ink-600 px-[13px] py-[7px] text-paper-100 [font:500_var(--text-xs)/1_var(--font-mono)] [letter-spacing:var(--tracking-mono)]">
							{tool}
						</li>
					))
				}
			</ul>
			<p class="mt-5 text-ink-400 [font:var(--type-mono-meta)]">
				this site = Astro · GSAP · Lenis
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
